  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the yakimono grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Trim the eggplants to 1-inch thick slices.",
    "Brush both sides of the eggplant slices with olive oil and season with salt, pepper, oregano, and thyme.",
    "Grill the eggplant slices for 3-4 minutes per side or until tender and lightly charred.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together garlic ginger paste and lemon juice.",
    "Once the eggplant is cooked, brush it with the garlic ginger paste mixture on both sides.",
    "Serve the eggplant slices hot, garnished with chopped parsley and a squeeze of fresh lemon juice."
